height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	b.<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">用小于</span>0.28MPa<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">干燥空气沿与吸入空气相反方向吹，喷嘴与折叠纸少相距</span>25<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">毫米，并沿其长度方向上、下吹。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	c.<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">滤芯上有油脂，则应溶有无泡沫洗涤剂温水中洗，此温水中至少将滤芯浸渍</span>15<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">分钟，并用软管中干净水拎洗，不要用加热方法使其加速干燥，一只滤芯可洗</span>5<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">次，然后丢弃不可再用。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	d.<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">滤芯内放一灯进行检查，如发现变薄，针孔或破损之处应废弃不用。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">三、冷却器</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">冷却器管子内，外表面要特别留意决对保持清洁，否则将降低冷却效果，应工作条件，定期清洁。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">四、储气罐</span>/<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">油气分离器</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">储气罐</span>/<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">油气分离器按压力容器标准制造和验收，不任意修改。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">五、安全阀</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">装于储气罐</span>/<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">油气分离器上安全阀每年至少检查一次，调整安全阀要有专业人负责进行，每三个月至少要拉松一下杠杆一次，使阀开启和关闭一次，一确保安全阀能正常工作。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">检验步骤如下：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	a.<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">关闭供气阀；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	b.<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">接通水源；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	c.<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">启动机组；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	d.<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">观察工作压力，慢慢顺时针方向旋转压力调节器调节螺栓，当压力达到规定数值时，安全阀还未打开或达至规定值前已打开，则必须调整之。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">调整步骤如下：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	a.<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">卸下帽盖和铅封；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	b.<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">阀开启过早，则松开锁紧螺母并旋紧定位螺栓半圈，阀开过迟则松开锁</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">紧螺母约一圈并松开定位螺栓半圈。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	c.<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">重复检测步骤，安全阀规定压力值时，仍不能打开，则再次调整之。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">六、数显温度计实验</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">数显温度计检验方法是将其热电偶与一支可靠温度计一起放油浴内，若温度偏差大于或等于&plusmn;</span>5%<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，则应更换此温度计。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">七、电机过载继电器</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">继电器正常情况下，触点应是闭合，当电流超过额定值时打开，切断电机电源。</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">下面是海普润空压机为大家总结的一些知识点，希望能为大家提供帮助。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一、空压机的压力调节器整定</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">卸载压力用上调节螺栓来进行调整，将螺栓顺时针旋转，卸载压力提高，逆时针旋转卸载压力降低。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">二、空气滤清器</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">吸入空气中灰尘被阻隔滤清器中，以避免压缩机被过早磨损和油分离器被阻塞，通常运转</span>1000<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个小时或一年后，要更换滤芯，多灰尘区，则更换时间间隔要缩短。滤清器维修时必须停机，减少停车时间，建议换上一个新或已清洁过备用滤芯。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">清洁滤芯步骤如下：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	a.<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对着一个平面轮流轻敲滤芯两端面，以绝大部分重而干灰沙。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	b.<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">用小于</span>0.28MPa<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">干燥空气沿与吸入空气相反方向吹，喷嘴与折叠纸少相距</span>25<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">毫米，并沿其长度方向上、下吹。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	c.<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">滤芯上有油脂，则应溶有无泡沫洗涤剂温水中洗，此温水中至少将滤芯浸渍</span>15<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">分钟，并用软管中干净水拎洗，不要用加热方法使其加速干燥，一只滤芯可洗</span>5<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">次，然后丢弃不可再用。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	d.<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">滤芯内放一灯进行检查，如发现变薄，针孔或破损之处应废弃不用。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">三、冷却器</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">冷却器管子内，外表面要特别留意决对保持清洁，否则将降低冷却效果，应工作条件，定期清洁。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">四、储气罐</span>/<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">油气分离器</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">储气罐</span>/<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">油气分离器按压力容器标准制造和验收，不任意修改。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">五、安全阀</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">装于储气罐</span>/<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">油气分离器上安全阀每年至少检查一次，调整安全阀要有专业人负责进行，每三个月至少要拉松一下杠杆一次，使阀开启和关闭一次，一确保安全阀能正常工作。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">检验步骤如下：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	a.<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">关闭供气阀；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	b.<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">接通水源；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	c.<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">启动机组；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	d.<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">观察工作压力，慢慢顺时针方向旋转压力调节器调节螺栓，当压力达到规定数值时，安全阀还未打开或达至规定值前已打开，则必须调整之。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">调整步骤如下：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	a.<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">卸下帽盖和铅封；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	b.<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">阀开启过早，则松开锁紧螺母并旋紧定位螺栓半圈，阀开过迟则松开锁</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">紧螺母约一圈并松开定位螺栓半圈。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	c.<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">重复检测步骤，安全阀规定压力值时，仍不能打开，则再次调整之。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">六、数显温度计实验</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">数显温度计检验方法是将其热电偶与一支可靠温度计一起放油浴内，若温度偏差大于或等于&plusmn;</span>5%<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，则应更换此温度计。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">七、电机过载继电器</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">继电器正常情况下，触点应是闭合，当电流超过额定值时打开，切断电机电源。</span></p>\r\n','','','127.0.0.1'),(27,37,'<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; text-indent: 50px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold;\">不买贵的，适合自己的才是做好的。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; text-indent: 47px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">适合自己</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">空压机</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">的才是最好的，对于空压机的配置选择上，用户难免看花眼，把握自己的需求，结合自己小型喷漆用途：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; text-indent: 47px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">第一、从整个空压机的发展趋势来看，由于螺杆机的气量更为稳定，喷漆质量更好。</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; font-weight: bold;\">锁定螺杆</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; font-weight: bold;\">空压</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; font-weight: bold;\">机。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; text-indent: 47px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">第二、确定喷漆气枪的</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">用</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">气量要求，一般小于3把气枪选定空压机功率为5.5kw，气压在0.4-0.7mPa即可。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; text-indent: 47px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">第三、结合小企业，对成本</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">控制</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">把关计算，前期购买成本和后期维护及用电成本，都要详细考虑到，下图是空压机的费用构成比例，可见选用节能省电的空压机才是最省钱的空压机。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; text-indent: 47px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; text-indent: 35px;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/uploads/allimg/150831/1-150S1124U3L3.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 674px; height: 900px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; text-indent: 35px;\">\r\n	&nbsp;海普润空压机</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; text-indent: 47px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">第四、结合小企业，为充分利用工作空间，要选取噪音低</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">、占地小的空</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">压机。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; text-indent: 47px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">第五、提高效率，减少维护成本，选用智能的空压机。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; text-indent: 47px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">综合考虑各方面，前期投资成本和后期的能耗、保养费用等都是需要考虑的因素，不盲目选择国外品牌，目前很多国内一线品牌无论从质量还是服务都毫不逊色，对于小企业喷漆用途来说</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">，省购买成本、节省保养维护费用，节省电费的空压机</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">才是最适合自己的。推荐海普润5.5kw一体</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">空压</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">机，结构紧凑，省电省心，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">空压机价格优惠</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">。</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">此外，用空压机喷漆的做到匀称的操作要领：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; text-indent: 56px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">1、运枪行走速度要均匀一致，枪走直线；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; text-indent: 56px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">2、压搭要一致，每次压搭1/2；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; text-indent: 56px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">3、枪、物距离要保持一致，不得忽远忽近；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; text-indent: 56px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">4、每遍厚度要薄，最忌喷厚，容易出流坠；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; text-indent: 56px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">5、调漆稠度要合适，漆滴拖尾8-10毫米为宜，稠了起皱稀了流；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; text-indent: 56px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">6、潮湿季节喷漆必须添加催干剂。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; text-indent: 47px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n','','','127.0.0.1'),(28,37,'<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">随着变频空气压缩机的推广，变频空压机给用户带来方便带来省电的同时。变频螺杆空压机的变频器使用也会遇到一些常见故障及问题，这里海普润变频空压机给出这十大问题的原因及解决方案。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">古有十大酷刑，让人求生不能，求死不得，饱受人间炼狱；今有变频器的十大&ldquo;酷刑&rdquo;，同样可让你的变频器遭遇痛苦。下面跟着小编捋一捋哪些十大&ldquo;酷刑&rdquo;会让你的变频器&ldquo;生不如死&rdquo;<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">!</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　变频器的十大&ldquo;酷刑&rdquo;之一：加载</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　长时间的负载过重，不仅会影响电机的寿命，同时将损坏你的变频器，缩短变频器的使用寿命。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　变频器的十大&ldquo;酷刑&rdquo;之二：桑拿</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　周围温度过高，风机堵转，温度传感器性能不良，马达过热。从来不给变频器做维护，变频器也需要经常的、周期的维护和保养。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　变频器的十大&ldquo;酷刑&rdquo;之三：欠压</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　电源电压、发电机组电压不够，变频器频繁欠压，容易导致内部元件损坏<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">!</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　变频器的十大&ldquo;酷刑&rdquo;之四：淋雨</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　变频器安装调试前，处于潮湿的环境；变频器运行后，工作环境比较恶劣，时不时有雨水进入变频器，变频器的电器元件长期处于潮湿环境中，对其线路板大大不利。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　变频器的十大&ldquo;酷刑&rdquo;之五：雷击</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　没有按照设备厂家的要求，未给变频器接地及装设避雷措施<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">!</span>导致雷雨交加时间变频器容易损坏。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　变频器的十大&ldquo;酷刑&rdquo;之六：过压</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　电源电压、发电机组电压过高，变频器长时间供电过高容易导致内部元件损坏<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">!</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　变频器的十大&ldquo;酷刑&rdquo;之七：腐蚀</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　因腐蚀性气体造成拨动开关，继电器接触不良，因腐蚀性气体造成晶体间短路，端子腐蚀造成主电路短路，线路板腐蚀造成各器件间短路。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　变频器的十大&ldquo;酷刑&rdquo;之八：蹦蹦床</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　所有变频器安装在同一刚性基础上，或基础过于薄弱，基础无法提供足够的强度，束缚变频器的运行振动，变频器就像在蹦床上一样，&ldquo;跳&rdquo;个不停。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　变频器的十大&ldquo;酷刑&rdquo;之九：冷暴力</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　变频器从来得不到足够的&ldquo;关心&rdquo;，使用者不按厂家要求检查和定期维护变频器，或很多年不更换风机，不给变频器吹灰，不检查螺丝的松动，使变频器从&ldquo;小病不治&rdquo;到&ldquo;不治的大病&rdquo;。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　变频器的十大&ldquo;酷刑&rdquo;之十：小马拉车</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　选型不准，会早造成变频器超载，小马拉大车现象，参数未调整到最佳使用状态，使变频器经常过流，过压等频繁跳保护，提前劳损、损坏。</span></p>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n','','','127.0.0.1'),(29,37,'<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; text-indent: 2em;\">\r\n	1、油气分离器质量；</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; text-indent: 2em;\">\r\n	2、回油管或回油单向阀堵塞；</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; text-indent: 2em;\">\r\n	3、压力维持阀开启压力过低；</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; text-indent: 2em;\">\r\n	4、使用压力过低；</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; text-indent: 2em;\">\r\n	5、油的品质出现泡沫。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; text-indent: 2em;\">\r\n	常见的压力阀设定在大于或者等于0.40Mpa出气，油气分离芯最好用原装的(内置的)回油管的位置有没有偏移，外置的要看一下回油管和滤网或者回油单向阀。空气压缩机压力维持阀流速过高，也会产生压缩空气含油量高的情况(开启压力过低)，这种情况经常出现。&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n','','','127.0.0.1'),(30,37,'<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; text-indent: 2em;\">\r\n	答：空压机相比同行业产品，具有十分明显的节能、高效、低噪特点。ODP系列高效节能电动机同等条件下节约电能30%，噪音低。采用德国GHH-RAND 最先进专利：5对6齿形，省电25%以上，面对面滚锥轴承，空气压缩比更高，同等条件下排气量较大，效率较高。与此同时空调式过滤网和油显示镜更精细更人性化的细节设计，尽显产品品质。</p>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n','','','127.0.0.1'),(31,37,'<span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24.5px; text-indent: 28px; word-spacing: -1.5px;\">答：正常情况下气压达到压力下限压缩机会自动加载，不加载的原因可能有这几种可能：气管路上压力低于压力调节器加载压力，电磁阀失灵，电脑板出现故障，油气分离器与卸荷阀间的控制管路上有泄漏。提醒：</span>空压机<span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24.5px; text-indent: 28px; word-spacing: -1.5px;\">在正常使用3000小时左右时，要整体检查，进行保养维护！</span>','','','127.0.0.1'),(32,37,'<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; text-indent: 2em;\">\r\n	答：螺杆压缩机正常运行一段时间后，突兀出现噪声增高现象时，可能会是排气端轴承损坏，压缩机运行过程中缺乏必要的冷凝液排放，导致排放管堵塞。</p>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n','','','127.0.0.1'),(33,37,'<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; text-indent: 2em;\">\r\n	答：冬季气温下降，空气压缩机因使用不当或者维护不及时，常会出现一些质量事故，造成重大的经济损失及安全隐患。开机前打开侧盖，观察油品是否有变浓或冻结现象，倘若有，必须先给油品加热，将空压机所有排气阀门打开，盘动大飞轮运转2-3圈后 ，空负载开机运行15分钟后，关上阀门，检查一、二级压力正常后进入正常供气状态。工作完毕将储气罐内余气放出并放掉冷却水。</p>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n','','','127.0.0.1'),(34,37,'<span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24.5px; text-indent: 28px; word-spacing: -1.5px;\">答：润滑油使用一定时间以后，由于摩擦表面磨损下的金属屑，机件上脱落的漆层，润滑油在冷却过程中产生水分、循环润滑过程中温度和其他影响使润滑性能渐次降低甚至变质。杂质在润滑油中易形成研磨膏类似物，污染润滑油，剧烈地加速机器摩擦表面的磨蚀。因此机器的润滑油在使用过程中若逐渐变质到下列指标就应该更换新油，倘若缺乏检验设备而无法检查是，每隔2000~3000小时，更换一次新油。并仔细清洗给油设备和各润滑点。</span>','','','127.0.0.1'),(35,37,'<span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24.5px; text-indent: 28px; word-spacing: -1.5px;\">答：要根据生产中所需的用气压力、用到设备上是固定作业还是移动作业，最后根据设备上标注的用气量选择能够满足生产需要的螺杆</span>压缩机<span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24.5px; text-indent: 28px; word-spacing: -1.5px;\">。一般情况下气源的输出压力应比气动系统中的最高工作压力高20%左右。</span>','','','127.0.0.1'),(36,37,'<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; text-indent: 2em;\">\r\n	答：常见的压力阀设定在大于或者等于0.4Mpa出气，油气分离芯最好是原装的，内置的回油管的位置有没有偏移，外置的回油管和滤网或者回油单向阀。空气压缩机压力维持阀流速过高，也会产生压缩空气含油量高的情况，这种情况经常出现。</p>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n','','','127.0.0.1'),(37,35,'<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; clear: both;\">\r\n	随着我国工业生产与环保体系建立越来越紧密的合作关系，行业也逐渐看到了节能降耗的巨大价值，近期国家推出了空气压缩机的新国标，使环保产业与工业生产的需求更快的结合到一起。智能与节能是多么熟悉的字眼，在我们生活中处处提倡节能环保，环境保护与节能减排已经成为刻不容缓的任务，如今考虑是如何才能更智能更节能。海普润空压机创业之初便投身于智能节能环保事业，由海普润研发制造稀土永磁变频空压机，通过最新的设计与改造，实现了海普润空压机的智能、高效、节能、低噪。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; clear: both; text-align: center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/uploads/allimg/150831/1-150S1125K6211.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 366px; height: 240px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; clear: both;\">\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; 海普润空压机在选型及设计方面有无与伦比的优势，单是节能就比普通空压机节省50%的电，使用寿命比普通空压机寿命长达5-10年，由于设计特点，海普润空压机改变传统空压机的很多细节，使产品更加人性化、智能化。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; clear: both; text-align: center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/uploads/allimg/150831/1-150S1125Jc20.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 513px; height: 513px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; word-spacing: -1.5px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; clear: both;\">\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; 通过客户多年的使用效果，海普润空压机得到了各企业的高度评价及肯定。海普润空压机凭着&ldquo;科技创新、以质取胜&rdquo;的企业精神，致力发展成为中国空压机领域最有影响力的智能型节能空压机品牌之一。</p>\r\n','',''